refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;

 voidmt_srand
 intnullseed&null;
 intmodeMT_RAND_MT19937



 Seeds the random number generator with
 seed or with a random value
 if no seed is given.


&note.randomseed;
&caution.mt19937-tiny-seed;

&reftitle.changelog;







     &Version;
     &Description;





     8.3.0

      seed is now nullable.




     7.1.0

      srand has been made an alias of mt_srand.




     7.1.0

      mt_rand has been updated to use the fixed, correct, version of
       the Mersenne Twister algorithm. To fall back to the old behaviour, use mt_srand with MT_RAND_PHP as the second parameter.
